longBusinessSummary: Li3 Lithium Corp., a junior exploration company, focuses on the exploration and development of lithium properties. It holds interest in the Mutare lithium project that covers an area of 1,500 hectares located within the Mutare Greenstone Belt of Zimbabwe; and Hard Rock Lithium project. The company was formerly known as Western Troy Capital Resources Inc. and changed its name to Li3 Lithium Corp. in August 2022. Li3 Lithium Corp. was incorporated in 1989 and is based in Toronto, Canada.
